query:
SELECT 
  p.id,
  p.addressLine1,
  p.city,
  p.owner1Name,
  GROUP_CONCAT(pt.tag SEPARATOR ', ') as tags
FROM properties p
LEFT JOIN propertyTags pt ON p.id = pt.propertyId
WHERE p.listName = 'Rolando'
GROUP BY p.id
LIMIT 10;
